room_title: Escape room "The Invitation" by Conquer the Chamber in Salt Lake City
room_description: Your eccentric neighbor, roy has always kept to himself. He hasn’t been the same since that mysterious accident that claimed the life of his wife. Rumors have spread that he’s becoming more and more detached from reality – obsessed over….something. He’s invited you over to his house and your intuition begs caution. However, what could this be about? Your curiosity is too overwhelming to turn this down…
